# EKS Pod Identity - Quick Knowledge Share

## Why Pod Identity?

Without Pod Identity:

```text
Pod
 ↓
Node IAM Role
 ↓
AWS Services
```

All pods on the node share the same AWS permissions.

With Pod Identity:

```text
Pod
 ↓
ServiceAccount
 ↓
Pod Identity Association
 ↓
IAM Role
 ↓
AWS Services
```

Each application gets its own IAM role and least-privilege access.

